text: Akhunovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Mikyashevsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 72 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 26 km from Davlekanovo, 6 km from Mikyashevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Davlekanovsky District
title: Akhunovo, Davlekanovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
